➖
Secret #72: Two hours before this photo shoot I found out my ex-boyfriend had another girlfriend...2 months later. Left with zero answers, I allowed this raging storm of emotion to transform my life. I used pain to empower my amazing life.
➖
How to Use Pain to Empower YOU:
▪️Find a passion.
▪️Travel by yourself.
▪️Live without expectations.
▪️Be selfish before you're selfless.
▪️Don't cheapen your experiences with cheap people.
▪️Don't sulk in the comfort of pain.
▪️Be a #YesGirl.
➖
